WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Connect your tools to RestoreAssist.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
Step 1: Open Integrations from the Settings menu.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
Step 2: Select your accounting software — Xero, MYOB, or QuickBooks — and authenticate in one click.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
Step 3: Choose your job management tool — ServiceM8, simPRO, or AroFlo.

00:32.000 --> 00:40.000
Step 4: Configure calendar and email sync.

00:40.000 --> 00:48.000
Your data flows automatically between platforms.

00:48.000 --> 00:51.500
All connected.